Package: montyhall
Title: Monty Hall Game Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package simulates the Monty Hall game. 
  The user selects a random door from 1-3. A goat door is selected.
  The user may change their selection. The selection will either be a goat door 
  or car door.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
Depends: dplyr

